$18) 18. Rd7 $14 Rxb6 $4 19. Rxa7 $18) 16. Qa4 Nb6 17. Qb4 Qh5 {[#]} ({Black's
queen had to move to the kingside, and not because there are attacking chances.
The exchange would have left White on top as is clearly seen in the following
line:} 17... Qxb4 18. cxb4 Rad8 (18... Rfd8 19. Be3 e5 20. Rxd8+ Rxd8 21. Bf1
$16 {1/2-1/2 (35) Wells,P (2530)-Lalic,B (2600) Szeged 1997}) 19. Be3 Rxd1+ 20.
