interesting problems for Black with this novelty. This pawn sacrifice is
directed to stop Black from blockading the queenside with Nc4.} e5 $1 (24...
Bxc4 25. Rc3 $1 {White's pressure along the c-file is going to cause problems
to Black.}) (24... Nxc4 $4 {is not possible as it loses a piece after} 25. Qc3
